---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Host a Scoreboard">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <header class="mb-10 border-b border-white/10 pb-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Host a CTF Scoreboard</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400">
        Ready to run a competition? Spin up your own scoreboard in seconds.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      
      <section class="cyber-card p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Run the Scoreboard</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-sm text-slate-300">
          <p>This command will start a CTF Scoreboard on port 4005.</p>
          
          <div class="mb-4">
            <pre class="bg-black/50 p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto"><code>docker run -d -p 4005:4005 joshbeck2024/ctf-cyberlessons-flag-scoreboard-public:latest</code></pre>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-blue-400 font-bold mb-2">Management Credentials</h3>
            <p>Username: <code class="text-cyber-primary">admin</code></p>
            <p>Password: <code class="text-cyber-primary">admin</code></p>
          </div>
          
          <p class="mt-4">
            It is preconfigured with the flags on this platform, but you can delete them and start over. 
            Once running, access the scoreboard at <a href="http://localhost:4005" class="text-cyber-primary hover:underline">http://localhost:4005</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cyber-card p-8 border-red-900/30">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-4">Cleanup</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-4">
          To stop and remove the scoreboard container:
        </p>
        <pre class="bg-black/50 p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto"><code>docker stop ctf-scoreboard && docker rm ctf-scoreboard</code></pre>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-2 italic">Note: Commands may vary based on your container name/ID.</p>     
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
